{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 300.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we were told to walk the streets in our best.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't but there was-- you know, the, the Jewish community has-- have got the clothes from the smaller ones to the bigger-- you know, from the bigger ones to the smaller ones and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was a sort of like a store where you would go, and you would be allotted what you needed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you outgrew-- left the thing that you outgrew, somebody else got.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, I wanted to bring to the attention of the world because if these are the, the, the commissions, as they call it, to do the inspection, well, please look a little bit deeper because this was no inspection, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a showplace put up for them, and they obviously swallowed it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were just spooned something which did not exist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After they left, the sardines were, of course, removed uneaten from those poor little kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least if they would have left them to eat it, they would have tasted it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And back to normal, which was, you know, they had the dirt and the-- and the, fleas and the, the lice and everything which got with it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the old people, which were terribly mistreated-- in, in a way mistreated because they were old and unable and, and just there wasn't enough to sustain them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which I think, when I'm looking forward, what I saw afterwards, and they died in Theresienstadt-- they were lucky.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was some time in '43, end of '43.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm pretty sure somewhere there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, that would be right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "October '44.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
